Class FortuneCookie

All Implemented Interfaces:
Placeable
public class FortuneCookie extends SimpleSlimefunItem<ItemConsumptionHandler>
The FortuneCookie is a rather simple SlimefunItem, it's a cookie which sends the Player who ate it a random text message. The messages can be defined in the LocalizationService.
